1) The solution must support missiles launched by the user.
-The Solution must initiate a missile launch when the user clicks the right mouse button or space bar. 
- No more than 5 active missiles at a time. 
A active missile is anyone that isn’t being used.
-When the missile is fired, if it doesn’t hit its target you can add a miss title while the missile is taken off of the active screen. 
-All missiles have same constant speed 
-The solution must launch missiles from the center of the bottom of the screen when a launch is initiated



